rComments: She is a really helpful prof, and her lectures reflect what will be on the quizzes and midterms. The only thing I hated about the class is that she makes you do a lot of group work, almost every other lecture. The group work even involved some acting....not what I like, but if you do, take her class, she's not a bad prof overall.
She's a very charismatic, clear, and eloquent professor. She makes the 3 hour lectures fly by. Definitely one of my favourite.

Professor McHugh was amazing! Take her class.  She was so nice and if you go to every class you will know EXACTLY what to do for all quizzes, exams, and essays.  She is one of the nicest profs I have ever met and the only prof I have ever had that can make a 3 hour lecture fly by! Take her class!! You won't regret it :)

She is a good professor, kinda reminded me more of a high school teacher because she is so eager to help. Very hard maker. High expectations. Seemed nervous and very rehearsed but attempted to make a boring class interested. I appreciated the effort she put in, but at the end of the day the class is still boring.
